Wikipedia:
Kapital (Capital) is a 1992 album by Laibach. It includes tracks such as "Wirtschaft ist tot" (Economy is Dead). Unusually, the LP, CD and cassette releases each contain different versions of every song. Track "Steel Trust" by Laibach sub-group Germania, appears only on LP and cassette.
